{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"MetricsStore\n            SQLite · EventEmitter\n          \n          \n            → sample events\n          \n          \n            \n              AnomalyDetectorlib/anomaly-detector.js→ fires RED event\n            \n            \n              Flow Nodenodes/perf-monitor/→ msg output\n            \n            \n              Report Page/performance-monitor/report→ chart.js + SSE\n            \n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A — Shared Store Hub (recommended)\n      All three subsystems consume MetricsStore. AnomalyDetector subscribes to store events, fires RED runtime events + triggers flow node alarm output. Report page queries store HTTP API. Flow node reads live sample.\n      \n        ProsSingle source of truthNo duplicationAnomaly detector reuses persistence\n        ConsAll three ship together","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1776161067826}
